Class Cabinet

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractFurniture
      • Cabinet
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Atreides, Luthien, Yossaria

    public class Cabinet
extends AbstractFurniture
    This class represents the idea for a cabinet line with basic representation of product details--height, width, depth, size, floor mount option, wall mount option, and earthquake safety requirement.
